Surrogate-enabled inverse UQ workflow

Requirements and Notes:
=======================
Please make sure the following environment variables are set, e.g.
export UQTK_INS=$HOME/research/UQTk-install
export PYTHONPATH="$PYTHONPATH:${UQTK_INS}"

Create an empty directory, cd there and run workflow.x as an example
Go through the steps of workflow.x
Create your own workflow for problem-specific model ensemble, data generation and problem-specific postprocessing


